        data-aos="fade-up"
      >
        CAMBIANDO VIDAS
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 text-slate-200 font-normal leading-relaxed"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="100"
      >
        Preparamos técnicos con integridad y valores para que brinden un
        servicio increíble.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 w-full"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        <a
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-primary text-brand-dark rounded-lg font-extrabold text-lg btn-shadow hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-95 transition-all text-center"
          href="https://funvalinternacional.org/preinscription-reference"
        >
          PREINSCRIPCIONES
        </a>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
          <a
            class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-5 bg-brand-blue/90 border border-white/20 text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-blue transition-all btn-shadow"
            href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=51946363540&text&type=phone_number&app_absent=0"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
              aria-hidden="true"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                fill="currentColor"
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M12 4a8 8 0 0 0-6.895 12.06l.569.718-.697 2.359 2.32-.648.379.243A8 8 0 1 0 12 4ZM2 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10a9.96 9.96 0 0 1-5.016-1.347l-4.948 1.382 1.426-4.829-.006-.007-.033-.055A9.958 9.958 0 0 1 2 12Z"
